# Cap Drupal

Capistrano drupal helpers

## Install

    # gem install cap-drupal


## Usage

	mkdir config
	cap-drupal  .
	cap multistage:prepare

Now you have this tree

	.
	+--- config
	|   +--- deploy
	|   |   +--- production.rb
	|   |   +--- development.rb
	|   |   +--- preview.rb
	|   +--- deploy.rb
	+--- Capfile
